e discussed in\nrelation with numerical and experimental studies of spin-Peierls systems.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 10 Nov 2004 09:22:58 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Tue, 12 Apr 2005 14:47:02 GMT"}],"update_date":"2007-05-23"}
